snippet.title: Terra Mango - A New Kind of Location-Based Game
snippet.description:
https://terramango.com/

ABOUT THE GAME:
Terra Mango™ is a new location-based MMORTS where you build virtual buildings where real buildings exist and battle with troops, in real space, in real time. Nearly every building can be captured and used to build your team’s civilization. You can capture your house, your neighborhood, your city… or maybe the world.

Coming soon to Android and iOS.
